en_567873_0	The International Cricket Council has given Sri Lanka a six-month deadline to conduct Sri Lanka Cricket Elections.
en_567873_1	The ICC said that failing which it would be forced to reconsider SLC’s membership status.
en_567873_2	This was announced following the ICC’s annual conference that concluded in Dublin.
en_567873_3	The SLC was represented by SLC Competent Authority, the Secretary to the Sports Ministry and SLC CEO Ashley de Silva at the ICC annual conference.
